---
title: Sesame Lime Chicken over Jasmine Rice with Sriracha Green Beans
description: Chicken breasts don’t have to be boring or plain: in this recipe, we’ve given them a vibrant sauce that leaps out with the Asian-inspired flavors of soy, lime, and sesame. We’ve also given the sides the flavor forward treatment—the rice also gets a burst of citrus while the green beans have a feisty dressing of peanuts, garlic, and sriracha. Altogether, this recipe adds up into something that’ll bring excitement to the table on any night.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/w44-r14-b9fec797.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/w44-r14-5b9be243ae08b532052e1422-d0f454b9.pdf
